data.eml:eml: Morphological redescription of Culex (Microculex) davisi and Cx. (Mcx.) imitator (Diptera: Culicidae) including structures and stages not previously described

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bangher, Debora Natalia, Stein, Marina (2017): Morphological redescription of Culex (Microculex) davisi and Cx. (Mcx.) imitator (Diptera: Culicidae) including structures and stages not previously described. Zootaxa 4347 (1): 56-70, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4347.1.3
